1- for build docker image : $ sudo docker build -t micro:latest .

2- for remove docker docker image : $ sudo docker rmi -f <docker image_id>

3- for inspect docker image : $ sudo docker inspect <docker image_id>

4- for run a command in a running container: $ sudo docker exec <docker image_id> tail -f /logs/cms.log

5 - for delete all your containers : $ sudo docker ps -q -a | xargs docker rm

6- docker run flask app : $ sudo docker run --name microblog -p 8080:5000 --rm micro:latest